---
title: Grilled BBQ-Spiced Chicken Salad with Homemade Ranch Dressing
description: This smoky grilled chicken on a fresh salad, smothered in ranch dressing, is not only quick and simple, it delivers on flavour too! Radishes and crispy shallots bring on crunchiness to compliment the cheddar cheese and creamy ranch.
